  "title": "MULTIPLE OPENINGS: Call Centre Assistant, $2.5K to $3,2K #HTJ",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> West / East<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,000 - $2,800 / MONTH<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday – Friday, 8.30am – 5.30pm</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Handle <strong>customer calls, emails, and order processing</strong> with accuracy and professionalism</li><li>Manage <strong>sales orders, client enquiries, and complaints</strong> promptly</li><li>Ensure all data is correctly documented in the system</li><li>Liaise closely with the operations team for issue resolution and order follow-up</li><li>Provide feedback and improvement suggestions to the team lead</li><li>Prepare ad-hoc reports and maintain updated information on products and pricing</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum NITEC / Diploma</li><li>Some experience in Call Centre/Customer Service would be good</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please send your resume to <em><strong>jalenetan@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>Jalene Tan<br />Outsourced Team<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
